data.description: This lovely home on a dead end street in PRP lives BIG! The room addition with deck provides plenty of room to spread out and the living room and partially finished (waterproofed) basement offers additional living space and possibilities. Original wood flooring and solid wood wainscoting add warm character and the kitchen with stainless appliances and open dining area are exactly what today's buyers are looking for. Venture outside and you'll be sold. The oversized lot has extra storage buildings and a garage that the resident mechanic will love.
